Mix 1/3 cup soup, 1/2 cup water, vegetables and margarine in saucepan. Heat to a boil. Remove from heat. Add stuffing. Mix lightly. Spoon stuffing mixture into greased 3-quart baking dish. Arrange chops over stuffing. Mix remaining soup and remaining water. Spoon over chops. Bake at 400 degrees F for 40 minutes or until chops are done.